OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,FAndrew Tate and his brother Tristan
OL,7,Fhave been arrested in the United
OL,8,FStates in connection with a UK police
OL,9,Finvestigation into a number of alleged
OL,10,Fsexual offences, Bedfordshire Police
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,14,Fsaid it was bringing further charges
OL,15,Fagainst the brothers ` who were
OL,16,Farrested by US Marshals in Miami on
OL,17,FSaturday ` in relation to allegations
OL,18,Ffrom four additional victims.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
