PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,FThe CPS said it has requested the
OL,7,Fextradition of the brothers from the
OL,8,FUS.
OL,10,FSocial media influencer Andrew Tate,
OL,11,F39, is charged with seven further
OL,12,Fcounts of rape, three counts of
OL,13,Farranging or facilitating trafficking
OL,14,Ffor sexual exploitation, three counts
OL,15,Fof assault occasioning actual bodily
OL,16,Fharm and 19 additional charges for
OL,17,Foffences relating to indecent images
OL,18,Fof a child and extreme pornography.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
