FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,FTristan Tate, 38, is charged with one
OL,7,Fcount of sexual assault, two counts of
OL,8,Frape and three counts of arranging or
OL,9,Ffacilitating trafficking for sexual
OL,10,Fexploitation.
OL,12,FThe CPS said the 38 additional
OL,13,Fcharges, in addition to 21 existing
OL,14,Fcharges, relate to alleged offences
OL,15,Fbetween July 2010 and August 2017.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
