PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,FMalcolm McHaffie, head of the special
OL,7,Fcrime division at the Crown
OL,8,FProsecution Service, said: "We have
OL,9,Fdecided to prosecute Andrew and
OL,10,FTristan Tate for further offences
OL,11,Fincluding rape, arranging or
OL,12,Ffacilitating trafficking for sexual
OL,13,Fexploitation and offences relating to
OL,14,Findecent images of a child.
OL,16,F"These charging decisions followed
OL,17,Freceipt of a further file of evidence
OL,18,Ffrom Bedfordshire Police and bring the
OL,19,Ftotal number of alleged victims in
OL,20,Fthis case to seven.
OL,26,@pD@\OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,F"The Crown Prosecution Service reminds
OL,7,Feveryone that criminal proceedings are
OL,8,Factive, and that these defendants have
OL,9,Fthe right to a fair trial.
OL,11,F"It is extremely important that there
OL,12,Fbe no reporting, commentary or sharing
OL,13,Fof information online which could in
OL,14,Fany way prejudice these proceedings.
OL,16,F"The CPS has requested the extradition
OL,17,Fof the Tates from the US. They have
OL,18,Fbeen arrested and await extradition
OL,19,Fproceedings to the UK."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
