PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,FBedfordshire Police said the
OL,7,FBedfordshire, Cambridgeshire and
OL,8,FHertfordshire Major Crime Unit had
OL,9,Fbeen continuing to investigate a
OL,10,Fnumber of other offences reported to
OL,11,Fboth them and Hertfordshire
OL,12,FConstabulary.
OL,14,FBedfordshire Police Assistant Chief
OL,15,FConstable Karena Thomas said:
OL,16,F"Officers from our major crime unit
OL,17,Fhave been working closely alongside
OL,18,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service and both
OL,19,Fnational and international law
OL,20,Fenforcement agencies as part of this
OL,21,Fcomplex investigation.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,F"We understand the interest that this
OL,7,Fcase will generate, but we would urge
OL,8,Fthe public not to speculate and to
OL,9,Fallow the legal process to be carried
OL,10,Fout correctly.
OL,12,F"There is no place for male violence
OL,13,Fagainst women and girls, and we will
OL,14,Fcontinue to work tirelessly to support
OL,15,Fvictims and investigate all reports
OL,16,Fmade to us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
