CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,FJoseph McBride, a lawyer for the
OL,7,Fbrothers, described the new charges as
OL,8,F"filth and slander" designed to
OL,9,Fcounter defamation charges filed by
OL,10,Fthe Tates in the US.
OL,12,FHe told the Associated Press: "They're
OL,13,Fpulling out all the stops to make sure
OL,14,Fthese guys never get their day in
OL,15,Fcourt.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]tD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,F"We are confident that once a
OL,7,Fcompetent judge sees the facts, and
OL,8,Fonce the Department of Justice
OL,9,Fconfronts this egregious abuse of its
OL,10,Fown authority, Andrew and Tristan Tate
OL,11,Fwill walk free. America does not do
OL,12,FBritain's political dirty work."
OL,14,FThe brothers are facing legal
OL,15,Fproceedings in Romania, where they
OL,16,Fcurrently live, and were facing
OL,17,Fextradition to the UK upon their
OL,18,Fcompletion after Bedfordshire Police
OL,19,Fsecured European arrest warrants for
OL,20,Fthe pair in 2024.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
