CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784548078
OL,3,CAndrew and Tristan Tate arrested in
OL,4,CMiami amid new sexual offence charges
OL,6,FThe pair have previously
OL,7,F"unequivocally" denied wrongdoing,
OL,8,Fwith Andrew Tate describing himself
OL,9,Fand his brother as "very innocent men".
OL,11,FIn June, their bid to bring a legal
OL,12,Fchallenge against the CPS after it did
OL,13,Fnot disclose the names of their
OL,14,Falleged victims in UK criminal
OL,15,Fproceedings was thrown out by a High
OL,16,FCourt judge.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@OO]qD@TOUqD@fO]
